Maynas, District of Iquitos, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Río">Rio</normalizedToken>
Nanay, quebrada de 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Morropón">Morropon</normalizedToken>
, inundated bank, ca. 90 m, 14 Feb 1985, fr., 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">M. Rimachi Y. 7755</emphasis>
(US!; IBE).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
